37 with the Rogue-South Coast Multi-Species Conservation and Management Plan the commission
38 adopted in December 2021, as subsequently amended by the commission.
39 (c) The commission may amend the plan as needed.
40 (d) The commission shall make the current version of the plan publicly available on a website
41 of the commission or of the State Department of Fish and Wildlife.
42 (15) The Marine Fisheries Enhancement Fund Subaccount is established in the Fish and Wildlife
43 Account. All moneys received by the commission from the sale of annual or daily ocean endorse-
44 ments under ORS 496.146 shall be deposited in the subaccount. Moneys in the subaccount may be
45 expended only to promote and enhance marine fisheries and marine conservation.
